Package org.hms.services.medicalrecord

Class MedicalEntry

java.lang.Object
org.hms.entities.AbstractTableEntry
org.hms.services.medicalrecord.MedicalEntry
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class MedicalEntry extends AbstractTableEntry
The MedicalEntry class represents a record of a medical consultation which includes details such as patient ID, doctor ID, date of consultation, diagnosis, treatment plan, and consultation notes.
